This is a linear surf map with a checkpoint half way through. Stage/part 1 is max speed most of the time and stage/part 2 is a bit slower with more obstacles. The map was made for timer servers so there isn't much to do after beating it other than learning shortcuts and getting better times. I may release the full version in the future with bonuses, secrets, and extras at the end but it's very unlikely since I don't have much free time anymore.

Entropy:A measure of the disorder or randomness in a closed system.

The map's theme is to progress in chaotic textures / surfing as you progress through the levels, causing more distress.

Changes from entropy:

Level one is completely open ended (I've beaten it five different ways as of today).
Level two has been redone almost totally.
Level three has a longer ramp and less beams to avoid.
Level four has a larger hole to surf through at the beginning.
Level five was turned into a nice bhop air strafe and made considerably easier.

Jail:
Time expire jail is a minigame.
Winner jail is a kill button
Secret winner jail (requires two buttons) activates 5 buttons for fun

My biggest inspiration in this map was the surf_buck series made by bucknasty, simply because he makes the most detailed maps that are fun and still look great to play on, unlike maps like surf_greatriver (no offence intended). I don't know why the water flickers at spawn, that is one bug that i couldn't fix and tried many times, it would look cool if you were stoned though. The only bug i can think of is the water in between spawn, which is actually put there on purpose, to trick faggots who think camping in between spawn is cool, I also made it amazingly close to impossible to shoot through top of jail, since i covered it with the perfect water texture. There is only one awp in the map, located at the very top, also a bombsite there, the objective is obviously to plant the bomb at the very top of the map and the ct's to surf there and defuse it, however thats not always the case, since there are a few secrets throughout the map that only the lucky ones will find. Most of all, enjoy the map.

****Put map in local disk/program files/steam/steamapps/*whateverthefuckyouraccountnameis*/counterstrikesource/cstrike/maps

Do not decompile this map unless you ask for permission.

This map is designed to become harder as time progresses. The blue ramps disappear first, followed by the green, then red ramps. The last player remaining aloft is the winner. As a player loses they are teleported to jail, where they are given a knife. The winner simply pushes a button to kill everyone.

** Requires NoBlock.
** Anti-AFK design prevents respawn.
